---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/hero.astro";
import Image_container from "../components/Image_container.astro";
import Included from "../components/included.astro";
import EquipmentItem from "../components/equipment_item.astro";
import "../styles/facility.css";

const theme = "facilities";
---

<Layout theme={theme}>
  <Hero
    video="/assets/imgs/video/wood_workshop_video.mp4"
    title="Workshops"
    description="Trifolium offers modern, flexible facilities designed to support collaboration, innovation, and community across all activities and events."
    poster="/assets/imgs/lazyload/workshops_lazyload.webp"
  />

  <section class="img_w_txt">
    <div class="txt_box">
      <h2>Workshops That Support Real Work</h2>
      <p>
        Trifolium’s workshops are designed for professionals who build things
        that matter. Whether you work in interiors, architecture, prototyping,
        or fabrication, we aim to cover your full production needs.
        <br /><br />
        With dedicated spaces for wood, metal, textiles, electronics, and model-making,
        plus access to digital tools and training, everything you need is right here—under
        one roof.
      </p>
    </div>
    <Image_container
      src="/assets/imgs/wrk_realwork.webp"
      alt="alex working on a table"
      labelLeft="assembly area"
      labelRight="1st Floor"
    />
  </section>
  <div class="logo_divider">
    <img src="../assets/imgs/logo_icon.svg" alt="" />
  </div>
  <section>
    <h2>Wood Workshop</h2>
    <Image_container
      src="/assets/imgs/wrk_wood_thumbnail.webp"
      alt="wood workshop"
      labelLeft="wood workshop"
      labelRight="1st Floor"
    />
    <p>
      Our wood workshop is one of the central hubs of Trifolium. It’s set up to
      support everything from precision joinery and furniture to fast
      prototyping and custom installations.
    </p>
    <div class="image_scroll_facilities">
      <img src="/assets/imgs/wrk_wood1.webp" alt="wood workshop preview" />
      <img src="/assets/imgs/wrk_wood2.webp" alt="wood workshop preview" />
      <img src="/assets/imgs/wrk_wood3.webp" alt="wood workshop preview" />
      <img src="/assets/imgs/wrk_wood4.webp" alt="wood workshop preview" />
      <img src="/assets/imgs/wrk_wood5.webp" alt="wood workshop preview" />
    </div>
    <p>
      The space is laid out to keep things flowing—whether you're running a solo
      build or coordinating with a team. Workbenches, industrial machinery, and
      open layout make it easy to focus and execute at a professional level.
      <br /><br />
      It’s the go-to workshop for carpenters, designers, set builders, and anyone
      working seriously with timber and wood-based materials. Whether you work in
      rough cuts or refined details, you’ll find the tools and room to do it right.
    </p>
    <h5>Equipment</h5>
    <div class="equipment_container">
      <div class="equipment_scroll">
        <EquipmentItem
          ImgSrc="../assets/imgs/placeholder.png"
          AltTxt="desc"
          Name="Name"
          Amount="1x"
        />
        <EquipmentItem
          ImgSrc="../assets/imgs/placeholder.png"
          AltTxt="desc"
          Name="Name"
          Amount="1x"
        />
        <EquipmentItem
          ImgSrc="../assets/imgs/placeholder.png"
          AltTxt="desc"
          Name="Name"
          Amount="1x"
        />
        <EquipmentItem
          ImgSrc="../assets/imgs/placeholder.png"
          AltTxt="desc"
          Name="Name"
          Amount="1x"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h2>Metal Workshop</h2>
    <Image_container
      src="/assets/imgs/wrk_metal_thumbnail.webp"
      alt="Map of Trifolium"
      labelLeft="Metal workshop"
      labelRight="1st Floor"
    />
    <p>
      The metal workshop is where structure, function, and fire come together.
      This space supports welding, cutting, bending, and light-to-medium
      fabrication work across various metals.
    </p>
    <div class="image_scroll_facilities">
      <img src="/assets/imgs/wrk_metal1.webp" alt="metal workshop preview" />
      <img src="/assets/imgs/wrk_metal2.webp" alt="metal workshop preview" />
      <img src="/assets/imgs/wrk_metal3.webp" alt="metal workshop preview" />
      <img src="/assets/imgs/wrk_metal4.webp" alt="metal workshop preview" />
      <img src="/assets/imgs/wrk_metal5.webp" alt="metal workshop preview" />
    </div>
    <p>
      It’s a versatile environment for people working in furniture, installation
      design, mechanical structures, or prototyping that calls for more strength
      and precision.
      <br /><br />
      The layout makes it easy to move between tasks without friction. If your work
      involves steel, aluminum, or similar materials, this is where your build starts
      to take shape.
    </p>
    <h5>Equipment</h5>
    <div class="equipment_container">
      <div class="equipment_scroll">
        <EquipmentItem
          ImgSrc="../assets/imgs/placeholder.png"
          AltTxt="desc"
          Name="Name"
          Amount="1x"
        />
        <EquipmentItem
